item.title: CVE-2023-26222|2024-08-30T14:06:54.070Z -- tibco%20software%20inc. -- tibco%20ebx
item.description: The Web Application component of TIBCO Software Inc.'s TIBCO EBX and TIBCO Product and Service Catalog powered by TIBCO EBX contains an easily exploitable vulnerability that allows a low privileged attacker with network access to execute a stored XSS on the affected system. Affected releases are TIBCO Software Inc.'s TIBCO EBX: versions 5.9.22 and below, versions 6.0.13 and below and TIBCO Product and Service Catalog powered by TIBCO EBX: versions 5.0.0 and below.
